<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1460178-why-do-you-think-grisham-had-to-go-into-so">Why do you think Grisham had to go into so much detail about the war story? I don’t think it really was that relevant to the plot and was way too long and graphic. It was not his usual style and I was disappointed with the book.</a>
</div>
