<a href="/questions/1463577-the-details-about-the-war-were-riveting">The details about the war were riveting. However, the ending did not live up to the rest of the book. I was disappointed. I would give it 4 stars for the details of the war, and 2 stars for the ending. How do others feel?</a>
</div>
