<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/39088984-long-road-to-mercy"><img alt="Long Road to Mercy (Atlee Pine, #1)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1534902771l/39088984._SX98_.jpg" />
